          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Hot Cross Buns. A British home-cook's dish — the kind of recipe families adjust across generations. Adjustable for what you need."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Bread is mostly waiting. Mix, prove, shape, prove again, bake hot with steam."
          }
